Package net.ssehub.comani.analysis.variabilitychange.core

This package contains the core class for starting this analyzer.
Author:
Christian Kroeher
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ResultCollector
    This class is used to write the results of the analysis to files.

    There are two files that will be created: ComAn_Results.tsv: the general data extracted from each commit ComAn_Summary.tsv: the summary of the numbers, e.g.
    ResultVisualizer
    This class provides the capabilities for visualizing the analysis results created by the VariabilityChangeAnalyzer and saved as single result file by the ResultCollector.
    VariabilityChangeAnalyzer
    This class represents the main class of this analyzer.
